Body:
async with stream_from_subscription_transform(((x, 10) for x in [0, 1, 1, 0,
    1, 0, 4, 2, 1, 4, 2, 3, 3]), timeout=21, granularity=lambda a, b: abs(a -
    b) >= 2, granularity_timeout=41) as s:
    await s.expect_after(10, 0)
    await s.expect_after(41, 1)
    await s.expect_after(21, 4)
    await s.expect_after(21, 1)
    await s.expect_after(27, 3)
    await s.expect_after(41, 3)
    await s.expect_exit_after(0)
pytest.mark.trio
